PrecisOrder (a) approving the exclusion of certain employees and positions from the application of specified provisions of the Public Service Employment Act, and (b) enacting REGULATIONS ON THE EMPLOYMENT WITH STATISTICS CANADA FOR THE PURPOSE OF THE 2001 CENSUS, which are designed to facilitate the recruitment and employment of temporary staff needed for the collection and processing of census data in the year 2001, effective November 1, 1999.

precis:
Order (a) approving the exclusion of certain employees and positions from
the application of specified provisions of the Public Service Employment
Act, and (b) enacting REGULATIONS ON THE EMPLOYMENT WITH STATISTICS CANADA
FOR THE PURPOSE OF THE 2001 CENSUS, which are designed to facilitate the
recruitment and employment of temporary staff needed for the collection
and processing of census data in the year 2001, effective November 1, 1999.
